name: I've Lost Artoo! (V)
Text: 'Deploy on table.  If A Sith''s Plans not on table, may deploy it from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  Once per game, may take a device that deploys on a character and/or an Effect with ''skill'' in game text into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Whenever your character leaves table, may place all your devices and Effects on them in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
